cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper is about an object detector that uses attention mechanisms to selectively calculate only on the locations that contain meaningful and conducive information, effectively reducing the computational cost. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE), as well as multimedia (cs.MM) since object detection is a common task in multimedia analysis.
